        <custom_item>
          type            : AUDIT_EXCHANGE
          description     : "EX16-MB-000210 - Exchange Internet-facing Send connectors must specify a Smart Host."
          info            : "When identifying a 'Smart Host' for the email environment, a logical Send connector is the preferred method.

